  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Argentina</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CIPPEC will work up a publication for the use of the Argentinean authorities and school personal through consultations of education professionals and authorities, and organization&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s own researches and studies, in order &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;educational justice&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D; to realize in practice in case of underprivileged children. The publication will provide new and concrete tools to promote comprehensive reform of the education system, which would be needed in Argentina in order equal opportunities to materialize in regards education. The publication will be promoted amongst policymakers and those who work in the field of education through seminars held in eight Argentinean provinces, and through the media to the rest of the country.</narrative>
  </description>
